      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly a bit heartbroken to be letting this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy the ride. I\u2019ve treated this car like a member of the family\u2014always garage-kept and hand-washed every weekend. It\u2019s in absolutely stunning condition, looking and smelling just like it did the day it left the showroom. There might be a microscopic mark here or there from a stray pebble, but you\u2019d really have to go looking for them. It drives like an absolute dream and is ready for a new home where it'll be just as cherished. Come by, have a coffee, and let\u2019s get you behind the wheel!",
